{"tid":722994,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇餐廳同小店食物質素, 性價比係高, 即係價錢實惠又好好味","createTime":"2018-06-30T04:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T07:16:59.000Z","uid":74632,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2b643a9c500440a4dc699debf7c9abfa00f1f213","tid":722994,"uid":74632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T04:44:16.000Z","msg":"我自己分享下:<br />\n<br />\n中環<br />\n1.\t蘭芳園, 茄牛通加脆脆, 唔熱又唔使等位就good fit<br />\n2.\t永樂園熱狗, 食極都唔厭, 個汁其他地方搵唔到, 做Tea 一流<br />\n<br />\n荃灣<br />\n1.\t唯一同老闆娘米線, 湯底一流, 衰在咩時間去都要排隊<br />\n2.\t漁川米線, 個蕃茄紅衫魚湯米線勁正<br />\n<br />\n紅磡,土瓜灣<br />\n1.\t有間開左無耐串燒叫川味香, 抵食, 而且係幾好味<br />\n2.\t林記, 燒賣係唔知點解特別好味的, 豉油又特別香<br />\n3.\t林細泰國野, 的野好味, 消夜一流<br />\n<br />\n老尖<br />\n1.\tLa Vach, 冇menu,全場食同一款沙律/扒/薯條, 薯條任食<br />\n<br />\n元朗<br />\n1.     士林台灣麵, 又係湯底一流<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳<br />\n1.\tLardos, 個steak一流, 不過其他野可以唔使叫<br />\n<br />\n葵芳<br />\n1.\t金潮小廚, 野食獲氣好夠, 好味<br />\n<br />\n唸到係咁多, 有咩正野, 請講"},{"pid":"f91f81c44f0e811c64821c9773dcc17d0acaf671","tid":722994,"uid":189724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T04:50:30.000Z","msg":"ike aaaaaaaa"},{"pid":"cdc098c2a6a40f8dae95e55167754f8c05a0cb28","tid":722994,"uid":164729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T04:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6ae03995299befa35a9f4ff14f7b3e88c6c66d","tid":722994,"uid":74632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdc098c2a6a40f8dae95e55167754f8c05a0cb28","tid":722994,"uid":164729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T04:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T04:54:09.000Z","msg":"下次試下先"},{"pid":"4184df5c023582ecce21e4a846c9752c040d12aa","tid":722994,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T04:55:09.000Z","msg":"中環果兩間真心唔覺好食"},{"pid":"a5f4095345ab0e0d6ac30174e3270eff84701cda","ti